name: Rocket Game (djsojojojo)
description:
First game of my GameDev Studies.

Navigate through asteroid fields and collect stars along the way. Maybe you'll set a new highscore, if not, try again!

Controls: A - Left S - Brake D - Right Space - Boost

Please give me somekind of feedback after playing!

Left and right animation sucks at this moment, but maybe it will be fixed in future.

Thank you!
